{"abstract": "Thomas M. Rutledge\u2019s company may propose a full slate of replacement directors for its target and may have enlisted a powerful ally for a bid \u2014 both adept moves, says Jeffrey Goldfarb of Reuters Breakingviews.", "web_url": "https://dealbook.nytimes.com/2014/02/10/charter-c-e-o-is-pressing-all-the-right-buttons-on-time-warner-cable/", "snippet": "Thomas M. Rutledge\u2019s company may propose a full slate of replacement directors for its target and may have enlisted a powerful ally for a bid \u2014 both adept moves, says Jeffrey Goldfarb of Reuters Breakingviews.", "lead_paragraph": "Thomas M. Rutledge seems like a man on a mission. The U.S. cable operator he runs, Charter Communications, is preparing a slate of replacement directors for larger rival Time Warner Cable, the target of his $60 billion hostile bid. He may also have roped in Comcast to alleviate financial worries about the plan to take over his former employer.", "source": "The New York Times", "multimedia": [{"rank": 0, "subtype": "xlarge", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/02/12/business/dbpix-breakingviews-charter/dbpix-breakingviews-charter-articleLarge.jpg", "height": 808, "width": 600, "subType": "xlarge", "crop_name": "articleLarge", "legacy": {"xlarge": "images/2014/02/12/business/dbpix-breakingviews-charter/dbpix-breakingviews-charter-articleLarge.jpg", "xlargewidth": 600, "xlargeheight": 808}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "jumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/02/12/business/dbpix-breakingviews-charter/dbpix-breakingviews-charter-jumbo.jpg", "height": 1024, "width": 761, "subType": "jumbo", "crop_name": "jumbo", "legacy": {}}, {"rank": 0, "subtype": "superJumbo", "caption": null, "credit": null, "type": "image", "url": "images/2014/02/12/business/dbpix-breakingviews-charter/dbpix-breakingviews-charter-superJumbo.jpg", "height": 2048, "width": 1522, "subType": "superJumbo", "crop_name": "superJumbo", "le